# api-endpoints

Core Meeting Management Endpoints:
`/api/v1/meetings/`

1. Meeting Bundle Processing
- Multi-source transcript integration (Teams + Pocket)
- Automated signal extraction with categorization
- Mind map generation from meeting content
- Importance Score: 85

2. Signal Processing Pipeline
`/api/v1/signals/`
- Domain-specific signal categorization (decisions, actions, blockers, risks)
- Signal status lifecycle management  
- Custom confidence scoring based on user feedback
- DIKW hierarchy promotion tracking
- Importance Score: 90

3. Knowledge Graph Integration
`/api/v1/knowledge/`
- Semantic relationship mapping between meetings and documents
- Auto-generated context links based on content similarity
- Cross-reference tracking with versioning
- Importance Score: 80

4. Document Management 
`/api/v1/documents/`
- Template-based document processing
- Automated metadata extraction
- Content relationship discovery
- Integration with meeting context
- Importance Score: 75

Key Workflows:
1. Meeting Capture → Signal Extraction → Knowledge Integration
2. Document Upload → Relationship Mapping → Context Building
3. Signal Collection → Status Tracking → DIKW Promotion

